snippet.title: Soul Tide: Character Themed PV - Virgina
snippet.description:
Soul Tide is an upcoming anime dungeon RPG mobile game based on dungeon exploring, storytelling, and anime girl collections.

A Fiery Prayer (火塵の祈り)
Lyricists: Sisouja    kageteru (景輝)
Composer: YinXin Shi (音心 石)
PV Animator: Curiosity
